  "proof_boundary": "This artifact proves an exact all-n summand-shift identity and a complete compact relative bound for T=100, k>=300. It does not bound the v>=3/2 far tail, does not prove the dominant n=1 adjacent wall, does not prove cone entry, and does not prove RH or Lambda <= 0.",
